3)¤what their guardian has left them pursuant to Section 25(3).
.of
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
Subsection 2 Disposal also includes income from the acquired property
and what replaces such. This does not involve the right to take on debt
obligations.
.of
.br
.kp off
.kp on
Subsection 3 With the approval of the state administration, the
guardian may withdraw disposal from the legally incapable person if
such is necessary for the welfare of said person.
